  <para style="h">2 Peetero</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ebbaluwa ya Peetero Omutukuvu Eyookubiri</para>
  <para style="toc2">2 Peetero</para>
  <para style="toc3">2Pe</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ebbaluwa ya</para>
  <para style="mt1">Peetero</para>
  <para style="mt2">Omutukuvu Eyookubiri</para>
  <para style="imt">Ennyanjula</para>
  <para style="ip">Peetero Omutukuvu yawandiika ebbaluwa eno ng’ali kumpi n’okuttibwa olw’okuweereza Kristo, nga mu mwaka <char style="sc">ad</char> 67. Yagiwandiikira abakkiriza bonna. Mu bbaluwa muno, ayogera ku bizibu ebigenda okweyongera okubaawo ng’amaze okufa. Agumya abakkiriza beeyongerenga okunywerera n’okukulira mu Mwoyo Mutukuvu, nga bategeera obutuufu obuli mu Njiri ya Kristo enkakafu era ey’amazima. Abalabula beekuume abayigiriza ab’obulimba abagenda okulwanyisa amazima nga bakuza ebirowoozo byabwe okusinga ebyo Ekkanisa by’eyigiriza. N’akomerezaayo n’okuyigiriza nti Kristo agenda kukomawo azikirize ensi eno, noolwekyo tetusaanidde kugyemalirako.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:1">Bar 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 1:1">1Pe 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 3:21-26">Bar 3:21-26</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">d </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="TIT 2:13">Tit 2:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nze Simooni Peetero omuddu era omutume wa Yesu Kristo mpandiikira abo abaafuna okukkiriza okw’omuwendo nga ffe, mu butuukirivu bwa Katonda waffe era Omulokozi waffe Yesu Kristo, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 3:8">Baf 3:8</ref></char></note>ekisa n’emirembe byeyongerenga mu mmwe nga mutegeera Katonda ne Yesu Mukama waffe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Okuyita n’okulonda kwa Katonda</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1PE 1:5">1Pe 1:5</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 2:12">1Bs 2:12</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kubanga mu maanyi g’obwakatonda bwe, mwe twaweerwa ebintu byonna olw’obulamu buno n’okutya Katonda mu kumanya oyo eyatuyita olw’ekitiibwa kye n’obulungi bwe ye. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 7:1">2Ko 7:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 4:24">Bef 4:24</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 2:18-20">2Pe 2:18-20</ref></char></note>Ebyo bye byatuweesa ebisuubizo eby’omuwendo ebikulu, mu byo mulyoke mugabanire awamu obuzaaliranwa bw’obwakatonda, muwone okuzikirira okuva mu kwegomba okubi okw’omu nsi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 2:3">Bak 2:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Noolwekyo mufubenga nnyo, okukkiriza kwammwe mukwongereko obulungi, ne ku bulungi mwongereko okutegeera, <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 24:25">Bik 24:25</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 3</char></note>ne ku kutegeera mwongereko okwefuganga, ne ku kwefuganga mwongereko obugumiikiriza, ne ku bugumiikiriza mwongereko okutya Katonda, <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TH 3:12">1Bs 3:12</ref></char></note>ne ku kutya Katonda mwongereko okufaayo ku booluganda abalala bonna ne ku kufaayo ku booluganda bonna abalala mwongereko okwagalananga. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 15:2">Yk 15:2</ref>; <ref loc="TIT 3:14">Tit 3:14</ref></char></note>Kubanga bwe muba n’ebyo ne byeyongera obungi, bibafuula ba mugaso era ababala ebibala olw’okutegeera Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:11">1Yk 2:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 5:26">Bef 5:26</ref></char></note>Oyo atalina ebyo muzibe wa maaso era awunaawuna, era yeerabidde bwe yanaazibwako ebibi bye eby’edda.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2PE 3:17">2Pe 3:17</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kale, abooluganda mweyongerenga okunywerera mu kulondebwa kwammwe ne mu kuyitibwa kwammwe. Kubanga bwe munaakolanga bwe mutyo temulyesittala n’omulundi n’ogumu. <verse number="11" style="v"/>Era mulyanirizibwa n’essanyu lingi nnyo mu bwakabaka bwa Mukama waffe era Omulokozi waffe Yesu Kristo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 3:1">Baf 3:1</ref>; <ref loc="1JN 2:21">1Yk 2:21</ref></char>
    </note>Noolwekyo, ebyo nzija kubibajjukizanga buli kiseera, newaakubadde nga mubimanyi, era nga ddala munyweredde mu mazima ge mwategeera. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 5:1">2Ko 5:1</ref>, <ref loc="2CO 5:4">4</ref></char></note>Era ndowooza nti kiŋŋwanira nga nkyali mu mubiri guno, okubakubirizanga nga nneeyongera okubibajjukiza. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 4:6">2Ti 4:6</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 21:18">Yk 21:18</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 21:19">19</ref></char></note>Kubanga mmanyi nga nnaatera okuva mu mubiri guno, nga Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo bwe yantegeeza. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 9:31">Luk 9:31</ref></char></note>Kyenva nfuba ennyo okukola kyonna kye nsobola, ne bwe ndivaawo mube ng’ebyo byonna mubijjukira.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 17:1-8">Mat 17:1-8</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kubanga tetwagoberera ngero bugero ezaagunjibwa wabula twabategeeza ebyo bye twalabirako ddala, eby’amaanyi n’okukomawo kwa Mukama waffe Yesu Kristo, era n’obukulu bwe. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 3:17">Mat 3:17</ref></char></note>Kubanga Katonda Kitaffe yamuwa ekitiibwa n’ettendo, eddoboozi bwe lyawulikika okuva mu ggulu mu kitiibwa ekingi ekimasamasa nti, “Ono ye Mwana wange omwagalwa gwe nsanyukira ennyo.” <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 17:6">Mat 17:6</ref></char></note>Ffe bwe twali awamu naye ku lusozi olutukuvu, twawulirira ddala eddoboozi eryo eryava mu ggulu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:19 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 119:105">Zab 119:105</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 22:16">Kub 22:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kyetuvudde tweyongera okukakasa ebyo bannabbi bye baategeeza, era bwe munaabigonderanga munaabanga mukoze bulungi. Kubanga biri ng’ettaala eyaka mu kizikiza okutuusa obudde lwe bukya, emunyeenye ey’enkya n’eryoka eyaka mu mitima gyammwe. <verse number="20" style="v"/>Okusooka mukimanye nga buli bunnabbi obuli mu byawandiikibwa, tewali ayinza kubunnyonnyola ku bubwe yekka. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:21 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 3:16">2Ti 3:16</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2SA 23:2">2Sa 23:2</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 1:16">Bik 1:16</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 1:11">1Pe 1:11</ref></char></note>Kubanga bannabbi tebaayogeranga byabwe ku bwabwe, wabula baategeezanga ebyo Katonda bye yabalagiranga nga Mwoyo Mutukuvu bwe yabibawanga.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Abayigiriza ab’Obulimba</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="DEU 13:1-3">Ma 13:1-3</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 4:1">1Ti 4:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:4">Yud 4</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">d </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 6:20">1Ko 6:20</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naye waaliwo ne bannabbi ab’obulimba mu bantu, era nga bwe walibaawo abayigiriza ab’obulimba mu mmwe. Baliyingiza mu nkiso enjigiriza enkyamu etwala abantu mu kuzikirira. Balyegaana ne Mukama waffe, ne beereetako okuzikirira okw’amangu. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Abantu bangi baligoberera empisa zaabwe ez’obukaba ne bavumaganyisa ekkubo ery’amazima; <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 2:17">2Ko 2:17</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 2:5">1Bs 2:5</ref></char></note>balibafunamu amagoba mangi nga bakozesa ebigambo eby’obulimba olw’omululu gwabwe. Abo Katonda yabasalira dda omusango era n’okuzikirizibwa kwabwe tekubuusibwabuusibwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:4 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:6">Yud 6</ref>; <ref loc="REV 20:1">Kub 20:1</ref>, <ref loc="REV 20:2">2</ref></char>
    </note>Katonda teyasaasira bamalayika abaayonoona, wabula yabasuula mu lukonko oluwanvu olujjudde ekizikiza, gye bali, nga basibiddwa mu njegere nga balindirira olunaku olw’okusalirwako omusango. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 3:6">2Pe 3:6</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 11:7">Beb 11:7</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 3:20">1Pe 3:20</ref></char></note>N’ensi ey’edda teyagisaasira, n’aleeta amataba ku nsi okuzikiriza abo abataamutya, n’alokolako Nuuwa eyabuulira obutuukirivu wamu n’abalala musanvu. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:6 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 19:24">Lub 19:24</ref>, <ref loc="GEN 19:25">25</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 26:10">Kbl 26:10</ref>; <ref loc="JUD 1:7">Yud 7</ref></char></note>Era yasalira omusango abaali mu bibuga by’e Sodomu n’e Ggomola bwe yabazikiriza, ne bisirikka mu muliro, bw’atyo n’alaga ebyo ebigenda okutuuka ku buli atatya Katonda. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:7 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 19:16">Lub 19:16</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 3:17">2Pe 3:17</ref></char></note>Kyokka n’awonya Lutti, omutuukirivu, eyalumwanga ennyo olw’obulamu obw’abantu abo abajeemu. <verse number="8" style="v"/>Olw’okubanga yababeerangamu, buli lunaku, yalabanga era n’awuliranga ebikolwa eby’obujeemu bye baakolanga, ekyo ne kimuleetera okunyolwa mu mwoyo gwe omutuukirivu. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 10:13">1Ko 10:13</ref></char></note>Mukama amanyi okuwonya n’okuggya mu kugezesebwa abamutya, n’abonereza abatali bakkiriza okutuusa ku lunaku olw’okusalirako omusango, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 3:3">2Pe 3:3</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JUD 1:8">Yud 8</ref></char></note>n’okusingira ddala abo abagoberera okwegomba kwabwe okw’omubiri ne banyooma abakulembeze baabwe.</para>
  <para style="p">Tebaliiko kye batya, beerowoozaako bokka, era tebakwatibwa na nsonyi kuvuma baakitiibwa. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JUD 1:9">Yud 9</ref></char></note>Kyokka bo bamalayika newaakubadde be basinga abayigiriza abo amaanyi n’obuyinza, bwe batwala ensonga ezo eri Mukama waffe tebakozesa lulimi luvuma. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JUD 1:10">Yud 10</ref></char></note>Abantu bali bavuma ne bye batategeera, bali ng’ensolo obusolo ezitaliimu magezi ezikwatibwa okuttibwa ne zizikirizibwa; era nabo okufaanana ng’ensolo ezo, bagenda kuzikirizibwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 13:13">Bar 13:13</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 11:20">1Ko 11:20</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 11:21">21</ref>; <ref loc="JUD 1:12">Yud 12</ref></char>
    </note>Abantu abo bagenda kubonerezebwa olw’ebibi bye bakola. Kubanga buli lunaku bagoberera okwegomba kwabwe olw’okwesanyusa, era abantu abo bakwasa mmwe ensonyi era babaswaza bwe beegatta nammwe mu mbaga zammwe, nga bakola effujjo mu masanyu gaabwe. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:14 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 18 </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 3 </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 2:3">Bef 2:3</ref></char></note>Balina amaaso agajjude obukaba, tebalekaayo kukola kibi buli kiseera boonoona era basendasenda abatali banywevu, bajjudde omululu. Baana abaakolimirwa, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 22:4-20">Kbl 22:4-20</ref>; <ref loc="JUD 1:11">Yud 11</ref></char></note>abaakyama ne bava mu kkubo okufaanana nga Balamu mutabani wa Beyoli, eyayagala empeera ey’obutali butuukirivu. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="NUM 22:21-30">Kbl 22:21-30</ref></char></note>Kyokka endogoyi etayogera, Katonda bwe yagyogeza n’emumanya olw’obujeemu bwe n’eziyiza eddalu lya nnabbi oyo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:17 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:12">Yud 12</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:13">Yud 13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Abantu abo nzizi ezitaliimu mazzi. Bali ng’ebire ebitwalibwa embuyaga, era baterekeddwa ekifo eky’ekizikiza ekikutte be zigizigi. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JUD 1:16">Yud 16</ref></char></note>Boogera ebigambo eby’okwekuluntaza era ebitaliimu nsa. Mu kwegomba kw’omubiri ne mu bukaba bwabwe basendasenda abo abali okumpi n’okubadduka abakyatambulira mu kibi. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 8:34">Yk 8:34</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 6:16">Bar 6:16</ref></char></note>Babasuubiza eddembe, so nga bo bennyini baddu ba bikolwa ebibi eby’okuzikirira. Kubanga omuntu afuuka muddu w’ekyo ekimufuga. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:20 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:2">2Pe 1:2</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 12:45">Mat 12:45</ref></char></note>Era abantu bwe bategeera Mukama waffe era Omulokozi waffe Yesu Kristo, ne badduka okuva mu bintu ebyo eby’ensi ebyonoona era ebitwala abantu mu kuzikirira, ate ne bava awo ne babiddamu, bibasibira ddala era obulamu bwabwe bufuuka bubi nnyo okusinga bwe bwali okusooka. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 6:4-6">Beb 6:4-6</ref></char></note>Ekyandisinze be bantu abo obutategeerera ddala kkubo lya Mukama waffe ery’obutuukirivu, eriggya abantu mu kuzikirira, okusinga lwe bamala okulitegeera, ate ne bava ku biragiro ebitukuvu bye baaweebwa. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PRO 26:11">Nge 26:11</ref></char></note>Olugero olwagerebwa kyeluva lutuukirira ku bo olugamba nti, “Embwa eridde ebisesemye byayo,” na luno nti: “Embizzi eva okunaazibwa ezzeeyo okwekulukuunya mu bitosi.”</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Olunaku lwa Mukama</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2PE 1:13">2Pe 1:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Abaagalwa, eno y’ebbaluwa eyookubiri gye mbawandiikira. Mu bbaluwa zombi ngezezzaako okubakubiriza mutegeerere ddala ebyo ebituufu era ebisaana. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Mujjukire ebyo ebyayogerwa bannabbi abatukuvu n’ekiragiro kya Mukama waffe era Omulokozi waffe ekyaweebwa abatume bammwe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:3 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 4:1">1Ti 4:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2PE 2:10">2Pe 2:10</ref>; <ref loc="JUD 1:18">Yud 18</ref></char>
    </note>Ekisooka, mutegeerere ddala nga mu nnaku ez’oluvannyuma abantu abagoberera okwegomba kw’omubiri gwabwe balijja mu mmwe nga babasekerera, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:4 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 5:19">Is 5:19</ref>; <ref loc="EZK 12:22">Ez 12:22</ref>; <ref loc="MAT 24:48">Mat 24:48</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MRK 10:6">Mak 10:6</ref></char></note>nga bwe bagamba nti, “Eyasuubiza nti alijja, aluwa? Kubanga kasookedde bajjajjaffe bafa, ebintu byonna biri nga bwe byabanga okuva ensi lwe yatondebwa!” <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 1:6">Lub 1:6</ref>, <ref loc="GEN 1:9">9</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 11:3">Beb 11:3</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 24:2">Zab 24:2</ref></char></note>Beefuula abatamanyi nti edda Katonda yalagira bulagizi, era olw’ekigambo eggulu n’ensi ne bitondebwa. Olw’ekigambo kya Katonda ensi yatondebwa ng’eggyibwa mu mazzi era n’ebeera wakati w’amazzi. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GEN 7:21">Lub 7:21</ref>, <ref loc="GEN 7:22">22</ref></char></note>Era olw’ekigambo ekyo ensi eyo ey’edda, amazzi gaagisaanyaawo n’ezikirira. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 10, 12; <ref loc="2TH 1:7">2Bs 1:7</ref></char></note>Era olw’ekigambo ekyo, eggulu n’ensi ebiriwo kaakano bikuumibwa nga birindiridde okwokebwa omuliro ku lunaku olw’okusalirako omusango, n’okuzikirizibwa kw’abo abatatya Katonda.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 90:4">Zab 90:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naye, abooluganda, temusaana, kwerabira nti mu maaso ga Mukama emyaka olukumi giri ng’olunaku olumu, era n’olunaku olumu luli ng’emyaka olukumi.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">laba <char style="xt"><ref loc="PSA 90:4">Zab 90:4</ref></char></char></note> <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HAB 2:3">Kbk 2:3</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 10:37">Beb 10:37</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 2:4">Bar 2:4</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 2:4">1Ti 2:4</ref></char></note>Mukama waffe taludde kutuukiriza ekyo kye yasuubiza ng’abamu bwe balowooza. Wabula ye akyabagumiikiriza, nga tayagala muntu yenna kubula, naye bonna beenenye.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="LUK 12:39">Luk 12:39</ref>; <ref loc="1TH 5:2">1Bs 5:2</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 24:35">Mat 24:35</ref>; <ref loc="REV 21:1">Kub 21:1</ref></char>
    </note>Naye olunaku lwa Mukama waffe lulijja ng’omubbi bw’ajja nga tewali n’omu amanyi; eggulu lirivaawo nga liwuuma nnyo, n’ebiririko birizikirizibwa n’omuliro, era ensi n’ebintu ebigirimu birisirikka.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Kale obanga ebintu byonna bya kuzikirizibwa, mugwanidde kubeeranga bantu ba mpisa ntukuvu era abatya Katonda, <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:7">1Ko 1:7</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 50:3">Zab 50:3</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 10</char></note>nga mulindirira era nga mwegomba nnyo olunaku lwa Katonda okutuuka, olunaku obwengula bwonna<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:12 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">obwengula y’ensi yonna n’ebizungirizi awamu n’ebintu ebirala byonna ebiburimu</char></note> bwe buryokebwa ne buzikirizirwa n’ebiburimu ne bisaanuuka ne bisirikka. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 65:17">Is 65:17</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 66:22">66:22</ref>; <ref loc="REV 21:1">Kub 21:1</ref></char></note>Naye nga Katonda bwe yatusuubiza, tulindirira obwengula obuggya n’ensi empya omuli obutuukirivu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TH 3:13">1Bs 3:13</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kale, abaagalwa, nga bwe mulindirira ebintu ebyo okubaawo mufubenga nnyo okuba abalongoofu abataliiko kya kunenyezebwa nga mulina emirembe. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 2:4">Bar 2:4</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 9 </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 3:3">Bef 3:3</ref></char></note>Kyokka mulowoozenga ku kubonyaabonyezebwa okw’obulokozi bwa Mukama waffe, nga ne muganda waffe omwagalwa Pawulo kye yabategeeza mu bbaluwa ze yabawandiikira mu magezi Katonda ge yamuwa. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 2:14">2Pe 2:14</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 2</char></note>Weewaawo ebbaluwa ze zirimu bingi ebizibu okutegeera, kyokka buli lw’awandiika aba ayogera ku nsonga ezo; wabula bo abatamanyi era abatali banywevu babinnyonnyola nga bwe bannyonnyola ebyawandiikibwa ebirala ne beereetako okuzikirira.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1CO 10:12">1Ko 10:12</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2PE 2:18">2Pe 2:18</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="REV 2:5">Kub 2:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Kale, mmwe abaagalwa, ebyo nga bwe mubitegedde, mwekuume muleme kukyamizibwa abantu abo abajeemu, si kulwa nga babaleetera okugwa ne muva we munyweredde. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:11">2Pe 1:11</ref></char></note>Mweyongere okukula mu kisa ne mu kutegeera Mukama waffe era Omulokozi waffe Yesu Kristo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">Oyo aweebwenga ekitiibwa kaakano n’emirembe gyonna. Amiina.</para>
</usx>
